  "heading_path": "热力学第二定律 / 熵",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 99,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03143:65f9e6b8672a]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03144:3e946903e23d]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03145:4b37625daf8a]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03146:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03147:212c84dc27ac]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03148:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03149:ad3525babfa0]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03150:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03151:eca910867a6b]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03152:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03153:eb9635da7e94]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03154:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03155:6d3668d3090c]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03156:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03157:ad6af9b56ca6]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03158:9d64d396fd12]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03159:fcb1d46964e7]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03160:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n绝热容器中两杯水热容相同，由能量守恒得末态温度 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P03161:29f18c64be1f]]。熵是状态量，可让两杯水各自沿可逆等压路径计算：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03162:7f5a7395f313]]\n结果为正，符合熵增原理：有限温差传热是不可逆过程。注意热水熵减的绝对值小于冷水熵增——这正是”同样热量在低温下贡献更大熵变”的体现。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03163:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P03164:06b3847e1b6f]]{document}\n",
